 Q. Write a Python program that accepts an integer (n) and computes the value of n+nn+nnn.
-----------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Solution:

def fun(n):
    n_str=str(n)
    nn_str=n_str+n_str
    nnn_str=n_str+n_str+n_str
    return int(n_str)+int(nn_str)+int(nnn_str)

n=input("enter a integer value")
print(fun(n))
------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
Output:

enter a integer value 5
615

